LFNoise0					step noise

LFNoise0.ar(freq, mul, add)
LFNoise0.kr(freq, mul, add)

Generates random values at a rate.
freq - approximate rate at which to generate random values.

see also: LFDNoise0, LFNoise1, LFNoise2


